# Xcode user-specific state (cursor positions, breakpoints, view state).
# Project structure (project.pbxproj) IS committed.
*.xcodeproj/xcuserdata/
*.xcodeproj/project.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/

# Build artifacts from RosenpassFFI/build-xcframework.sh.
#
# We don't commit these because:
#   1. The .a static libs are ~35 MB each (~70 MB combined per rebuild)
#      — would bloat git history fast.
#   2. They're 100% reproducible from RosenpassFFI/src/ + a pinned Rust
#      toolchain. Run `cd RosenpassFFI && ./build-xcframework.sh --release`
#      to regenerate. The script auto-syncs the outputs into the
#      locations Xcode expects (CloakVPN/rosenpassffi.swift and
#      RosenpassFFI.xcframework next to the .xcodeproj).
#   3. Anyone cloning fresh runs setup once; iteration on Swift code
#      doesn't require rebuilding the FFI.
RosenpassFFI.xcframework/
CloakVPN/rosenpassffi.swift
